==PADLET big screen scroller

Install

Upload the code to somewhere on your sever

Create a database called 'padlet'

Create the database table with the following code;

CREATE TABLE `messages` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `subject` text,
  `body` text,
  `attachment` text,
  `author` text,
  `created` text,
  `modified` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=32039 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;



Make sure that the web server has write access to padlet.csv

Change the settings in the 'config' block on the index.php as needed

Various other settings can be fiddled with int he script section of index.php to change the scroll speed etc.
FOr more information see;
http://owlgraphic.com/owlcarousel/#customizing